//__It __is__ kind of obvious, though,__ observed his Slytherin part.
//__I mean, do you actually believe that under natural circumstances,
//anyone would end up as the last heir to a Most Ancient House AND Lord Voldemort
//killed his family AND he has to avenge his martial arts sensei? If anything I’d
